<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>My First Styled Page</title>

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: lightblue;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        h1 {
            color: darkblue;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        p {
            color: darkgreen;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px;
            border: 2px solid black;
        }

        .special {
            background-color: lightyellow;
            color: darkred;
        }

        .hobby {
            background-color: lightpink;
            color: purple;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <h1>My First Styled Page</h1>

    <p class="special">
        Hello! My name is Risalat. I am a student and I am learning HTML and CSS.
        I enjoy creating webpages and learning new computer skills.
    </p>

    <p class="hobby">
        My favorite hobby is using the internet and exploring new technology.
        I also like chatting with friends and learning cybersecurity basics.
    </p>

</body>
</html>